title: Mandelbrot Set vs Julia Set
preview: Probably, Mandelbrot set is the most popular fractal. So many videos of Mandelbrot set
zoom are availabe. Julia set is not as popular as Mandelbrot set. But actually, it has
close relationship with Mandelbrot set. Recently, I rendered Mandelbrot set zoom
(at \( c_m \)) alongside Julia set zoom with varying control point (\(c_j\)).
